### Landing page
GET http://localhost:4000/

### Send a message via Slack
POST http://localhost:4000/api/slack/
content-type: application/json

{
    "channel_id": "sample",
    "text": "status"
}

### Send message via Telegram
POST http://localhost:4000/api/telegram/
content-type: application/json

{
    "message": {
        "from": {
            "id": "some_id"
        },
        "text": "/status"
    }
}